This layer depends on:

URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/poky
branch: master
revision: HEAD

URI: git://git.openembedded.net/meta-openembedded
branch: master
revision: HEAD

URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/meta-raspberrypi
branch: master
revision: HEAD

Layer maintainer: Philipp Wagner <mail@philipp-wagner.com>


This layer provides everything to build and develop Firefox OS for 
Raspberry Pi.

- Two recipes to create SD-card images for a complete system with 
  Firefox OS: a "production" one and one with additional development
  tools.
  -> see rpi-b2g-image and rpi-b2g-dev-image

- A SDK containing a cross-toolchain as well as all necessary libraries
  to build the Mozilla source code.
  -> see meta-b2g-sdk

